Power has been restored to certain areas of Tshwane. This comes after a switch tripped at the Njala station near Rietvlei earlier this morning. Courtesy #DStv403 PRETORIA - Power has been restored to certain areas of Tshwane. This comes after a switch tripped at the Njala station near Rietvlei earlier on Monday morning. READ: 3 TMPD officers, suspected drunk driver die in crash Authorities say power will be restored to all affected areas by the afternoon. Areas affected included Mooikloof to Pyramid, Centurion, Wingate and Claudius. 